Since you&#39;re using the Firebase-UI library, when you&#39;re using the following method call:

    .setQuery(query, ServiceOrder.class)

It means that you&#39;re trying to map all documents that are returned by the query into objects of type `ServiceOrder`. But this is actually not possible because your actual document looks like this:

    clienteTeste (document)
      |
      --- ServiceOrder (map)
            |
            --- client: {...} (map)
